{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442650/extras/WIDE_DAY_IMAGE_1.png?t=1727195501\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442650/extras/cultclassic.png?t=1727195501\" /><br>White Day VR: The Courage Test is an immersive VR experience that sees players returning to Yeondu High School in the dead of night to take on a chilling challenge unlike any other. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442650/extras/courage-test.png?t=1727195501\" /><br>In order to gain entry into the Occult Club students must undertake the &quot;Courage Test&quot;. But when senior Occult Club member Da-Hee Kim informs you that the test has been bought forward a day, how do you know if she can be trusted? <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442650/extras/WIDE_DAY_IMAGE_2.png?t=1727195501\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442650/extras/step-into-classroom.png?t=1727195501\" /><br>Long since closed after an unexplained accident, classroom 1-1 is now being used as a storeroom. Step into the eerie darkness and use the VR controller to interact with the decaying furniture inside and locate 15 hidden items.   <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442650/extras/timelimit-test-of-bravery.png?t=1727195501\" /><br>Challengers are given just 5 minutes to locate all of the items, but old furniture and hidden objects won't be the only thing you unearth in the dark...<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442650/extras/WIDE_DAY_IMAGE_3.png?t=1727195501\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442650/extras/multiple-endings.png?t=1727195501\" /><br>There are only ever two outcomes of the Courage Test: success or failure. Which ending will you discover?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442650/extras/chilling-visuals.png?t=1727195501\" /><br>Experience the horrors of the night school in terrifying detail in this high quality VR experience. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442650/extras/WIDE_DAY_IMAGE_5.png?t=1727195501\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442650/extras/3D-Sound.png?t=1727195501\" /><br>Hear every footstep, every creak and every unexplained noise in crisp three dimensional sound.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442650/extras/WIDE_DAY_IMAGE_4.png?t=1727195501\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442650/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1727195501","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442650/page.bg.jpg?t=1727195501","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442650/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1727195501","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442650/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1727195501","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Tracked Controller Support","id":52},{"description":"VR Only","id":54},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":"White Day VR: The Courage Test contains elements of the supernatural including ghosts, the ghosts of children and characters with mild disfigurement. There are some instances with blood but no excessive blood and gore."},"detailed_description":"<img class=\"bb_img\" s